App : Swiggy 

1. Security Risk:
User payment details or personal data may not be secure.
Impact: User data can be stolen and users may lose trust in the app.

2. Performance Risk:
The app may become slow when many users order food at the same time.
Impact: Users may not be able to place orders quickly.

3. Usability Risk: 
The app interface may be confusing for new users.
Impact: Users may face difficulty while searching food or placing an order.